section: compiler
synopsis: Completely refactor the handling of "known entities".  The goal is to
  make it possible to move code from one module to another within `ghc-internal`
  and `base` (or move code between those two libraries) without changing GHC
  itself.   This is a major step along the path to making `base` into an ordinary
  re-installable library.

  Mostly this change is only visible to authors of modules in `ghc-internal` or
  `base`.
